Package: rcsvw
Type: Package
Title: Read, Write and Validate CSV on the Web (CSVW)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Robert <robert_forkel@eva.mpg.de>
Maintainer: Robert <robert_forkel@eva.mpg.de>
Description: R implementation of the W3C CSV on the Web (CSVW) specifications.
    Allows loading metadata, reading and writing tables, validating schema constraints,
    checking primary/foreign keys, and converting data to JSON.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    readr,
    httr
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
